---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/main.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Enerama Environmental Technologies | PCT Patented Climate Control"
  description="PCT patented Liquid Desiccant climate platform. 30–70% energy savings, water recovery from air, field-proven across 14 years and 27 projects."
  canonicalPath="/"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative text-white py-20 lg:py-28" style="background-color: #0B3D4C;">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6 text-sm font-medium" style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);">
          PCT Patented · 14 Years Field Proven · 3 Countries
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6 text-balance">
          Liquid Desiccant Climate Infrastructure
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-200 mb-4 max-w-3xl">
          Replacing conventional HVAC in humidity-critical environments
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
          Enerama's patented Liquid Desiccant technology cuts energy consumption by 30–70%, generates water from air, and is field-proven across 14 years and 27 real projects.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a
            href="/technology"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
            style="background-color: #E07B39;"
          >
            Explore Our Technology
          </a>
          <a
            href="/investors"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold rounded-lg border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-[#0B3D4C] transition-colors"
          >
            View Investor Brief
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Proof Bar -->
  <section class="py-12 border-b" style="background-color: #1B3A6B;">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center">
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">350+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-300 mt-1">Installed Conditioners</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">2,830 kW</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-300 mt-1">Installed Power</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">11,792 L/h</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-300 mt-1">Water Extraction</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white">14 Years</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-300 mt-1">Continuous Operation</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem Section -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">
          Conventional HVAC Is Failing Industry
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Three converging crises demand a fundamentally different approach
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="p-8 rounded-lg border-2 border-gray-200 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6" style="background-color: rgba(224, 123, 57, 0.1);">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7" style="color: #E07B39;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Skyrocketing Energy Costs</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            HVAC accounts for 40–60% of industrial energy consumption. With energy prices up significantly since 2021, conventional systems are no longer economically viable.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 rounded-lg border-2 border-gray-200 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6" style="background-color: rgba(13, 115, 119, 0.1);">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7" style="color: #0D7377;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Global Water Scarcity</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Over 2 billion people face water stress. Industrial operations consume vast quantities — yet conventional HVAC recovers none of the moisture it extracts.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 rounded-lg border-2 border-gray-200 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6" style="background-color: rgba(27, 58, 107, 0.1);">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7" style="color: #1B3A6B;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Tighter Refrigerant Regulation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            EU and US regulations drive the transition away from high-GWP refrigerants. Facilities face compliance pressure and rising costs from conventional systems.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution Section -->
  <section class="py-20" style="background-color: #F9FAFB;">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide" style="background-color: rgba(224, 123, 57, 0.1); color: #E07B39;">
          THE DRAGON™ LIQUID DESICCANT PLATFORM
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">
          One Patented System. Three Problems Solved.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Enerama's Dragon™ Liquid Desiccant platform uses hygroscopic salt solution to absorb moisture from air independently — without mechanical compression refrigeration. The result: dramatically lower energy use, water recovery as a byproduct, and natural pathogen elimination.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #E07B39;">30–70%</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">less energy than conventional HVAC</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0D7377;">100+ L/h</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">clean water recovered from air per unit</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Natural</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">pathogen elimination — no UV, no chemical disinfectants</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0B3D4C;">50–70°C</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">low regeneration temperature — solar thermal compatible</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <a
          href="/technology"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white rounded-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
          style="background-color: #1B3A6B;"
        >
          See How the Technology Works →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process Steps -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">How Dragon Works</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">A four-step continuous cycle</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        {[
          { step: '1', title: 'Air Intake', desc: 'Ambient air enters the system' },
          { step: '2', title: 'Liquid Desiccant Absorption', desc: 'Moisture absorbed by hygroscopic solution' },
          { step: '3', title: 'Regeneration', desc: 'Solution heated, moisture released' },
          { step: '4', title: 'Water Recovery', desc: 'Pure water collected, solution recycled' },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4" style="background-color: #0D7377;">
              {item.step}
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">{item.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EPC Approach -->
  <section class="py-20" style="background-color: #1B3A6B;">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">
          We Do Not Deliver Products. We Deliver Results.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">Full EPC accountability — from design to commissioning</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-12">
        {[
          { title: 'Engineering', desc: 'We design the complete climate solution for your facility' },
          { title: 'Procurement', desc: 'We produce and supply all system components' },
          { title: 'Construction', desc: 'We install, integrate, and commission on-site' },
          { title: 'Support', desc: '60-Day Online Support after commissioning' },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/20">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-white">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <blockquote class="text-xl md:text-2xl italic text-gray-200 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
          "Other companies sell you equipment and leave. Enerama owns the outcome."
        </blockquote>
        <a
          href="/how-we-work"
          class="inline-flex items-center text-white font-semibold hover:text-[#E07B39] transition-colors"
        >
          How We Work →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Applications Preview -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">
          Built for Demanding Environments
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          27 projects deployed across 3 core industry sectors — applications designed for 10+ industries
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-4 mb-8">
        {[
          'Agriculture & Greenhouses',
          'Food Drying & Processing',
          'Data Centers & Technology',
          'Vertical Farming',
          'Pharmaceuticals',
          'Industrial Manufacturing',
        ].map((app) => (
          <div class="p-4 rounded-lg text-center border border-gray-200 hover:border-[#0D7377] transition-colors">
            <div class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #1B3A6B;">{app}</div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <a
          href="/applications"
          class="inline-flex items-center font-semibold hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity"
          style="color: #E07B39;"
        >
          See All Applications →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Track Record -->
  <section class="py-20" style="background-color: #F9FAFB;">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1B3A6B;">
          A Track Record Competitors Cannot Match
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          We are not a prototype. Enerama has 14 years of real-world results.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center shadow-sm">
          <div class="text-5xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #E07B39;">27</div>
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Projects</div>
          <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Commissioned across USA, Switzerland & Türkiye</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center shadow-sm">
          <div class="text-5xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #E07B39;">14+</div>
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Years</div>
          <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Continuous operation.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center shadow-sm">
          <div class="text-5xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #E07B39;">PCT</div>
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2" style="color: #1B3A6B;">Patent</div>
          <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Filed Q1 2026. Dragon Solar TES in pre-commercial development.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: #1B3A6B;">
        Ready to Transform Your Facility?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Talk to our engineering team about your specific requirements.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
          style="background-color: #E07B39;"
        >
          Request a Technical Demo
        </a>
        <a
          href="/investors"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold rounded-lg border-2 hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
          style="border-color: #1B3A6B; color: #1B3A6B;"
        >
          Investor Brief
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
